{"tid":775180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國欲與日本雙邊貿易談判 日促美重返TPP","createTime":"2018-08-11T03:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T10:24:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c08736c6d29b9a60ab30c5873d5b7929d0de8c2c","tid":775180,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"美國欲與日本雙邊貿易談判 日促美重返TPP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2134983/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%AC%B2%E8%88%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%9B%99%E9%82%8A%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%20%E6%97%A5%E4%BF%83%E7%BE%8E%E9%87%8D%E8%BF%94TPP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2134983%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AC%25B2%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%259B%2599%25E9%2582%258A%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E8%25AB%2587%25E5%2588%25A4%2520%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25BF%2594TPP&d=QBSkKEYAiAUBAIaFAeT1INtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f30d275d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2134983/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%AC%B2%E8%88%87%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%9B%99%E9%82%8A%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E8%AB%87%E5%88%A4%20%E6%97%A5%E4%BF%83%E7%BE%8E%E9%87%8D%E8%BF%94TPP</a><br />\n<br />\n美國與日本官員昨日會面，商討兩國貿易問題，但雙方貿易立場仍有分歧。美國則希望與日本展開雙邊貿易談判，惟日本卻希望美國重返跨太平洋夥伴關係協定（TPP）。<br />\n<br />\n日本經濟再生擔當相茂木敏充與美國貿易代表萊特希澤（Robert Lighthizer）會議，茂木敏充會後稱，雙方坦誠地交換意見，了解對方立場和想法差異，美國明確表示希望展開雙邊談判。<br />\n<br />\n茂木敏充又表達了日本的立場，稱TPP對日本和美國而言都是最理想，暗示希望美國重返TPP，進行多邊貿易談判。<br />\n<br />\n茂木敏充和萊特希澤今日進行第2日磋商，預料談及汽車業及農業議題。"},{"pid":"f8393526ce3de3acf5712cad21ee8697bf7194d0","tid":775180,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e3ac805616037aa0e370959de9b97340657eee","tid":775180,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"美日自己簽單邊自由貿易協定好過啦，當然日本肯定唔中意雙邊談判<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518588a2a508bc2d70490aa25e8c28b05cadc763","tid":775180,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:24:00.000Z","msg":"先跪低是常識"}]}